    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Apronio Pio <lb n="2"/>legato Augusti <lb n="3"/>pro praetore <lb n="4"/>clarissimo vi<lb break="no" n="5"/>ro consuli de<lb break="no" n="6"/>signato patro<lb break="no" n="7"/>no coloniarum <lb n="8"/>ob insignem er<lb break="no" n="9"/>ga cives beni<lb break="no" n="10"/>volentiam et <lb n="11"/>iustitiam eius <lb n="12"/>res publica <lb n="13"/>Siguitanorum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Der Geehrte war unter Severus Alexander (wohl in den Jahren um 225 n. Chr.) Statthalter von Numidien.</p>
            </div>
